Class DeliveryListDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.erp.light.view.dto.DeliveryListDTO

  • public class DeliveryListDTO
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a DTO representation of the entity DeliveryList.
    It is mainly used to transmit data between the frontend and backend.
    Author:
    Matthias Schnöll
